import React from 'react'

import './LinerProsentage.scss'



const LineerProsentage = ({prosentage = 80}) => {
    var ovals = [
        <div className="mx-1" />,
        <div className="mx-1" />,
        <div className="mx-1" />,
        <div className="mx-1" />,
        <div className="mx-1" />,
        <div className="mx-1" />,
        <div className="mx-1" />,
        <div className="mx-1" />,
        <div className="mx-1" />,
        <div className="mx-1" />
    ]
    for(let i=0; i<Math.floor(prosentage/10);i++){
        ovals[i]
    };
    return 
}

export default LineerProsentage
